{
  "id": "adv_event_2512_01_02",
  "title": "ドタバタ！？トラブルクリスマス！ 2話 プリンセスと共同生活",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、はい……分かりました",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio001.wav",
      "text": "みんなにも伝えておきます。それでは、失礼します",
      "startTime": 4.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4079.161119500001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui001.wav",
      "text": "今の電話はマネージャーさんからですか？",
      "startTime": 8.4458277862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええ。貴方達のことを心配していて",
      "startTime": 11.7124948343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio002.wav",
      "text": "後で様子を見に来るそうよ",
      "startTime": 15.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "マネージャーさん、優しいのね",
      "startTime": 17.65458107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui002.wav",
      "text": "みなさんも泊まる部屋やお風呂まで用意して下さって",
      "startTime": 20.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなに気にしないで。今はゆっくり休んで",
      "startTime": 24.4879137676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio003.wav",
      "text": "落ち着いたら改めて帰る方法を考えましょう",
      "startTime": 28.5666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとう",
      "startTime": 31.8329932054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui003.wav",
      "text": "知らない場所に飛ばされて不安だったけど……",
      "startTime": 33.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央さんのような冷静沈着でしっかりした人と",
      "startTime": 36.1663273017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui004.wav",
      "text": "出会えたのは不幸中の幸いってやつね",
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "褒め過ぎよ。……まあ、確かに私は",
      "startTime": 43.5663262845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio004.wav",
      "text": "普段から取り乱さないように心がけているけど",
      "startTime": 47.6999994915,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3209.2747688000004
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5080.000508499999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6990.000508499996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はあ～、いいお湯だったよ～。お風呂ありがとー！",
      "startTime": 50.9092742603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
