      "text": "あれ？　何話してるの？",
      "startTime": 56.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio005.wav",
      "text": "貴方達の今後について……って、どうして裸なのよ！",
      "startTime": 58.5092729886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-lala002.wav",
      "text": "お風呂上がりなんだから裸なのは当たり前だよ～",
      "startTime": 63.419340086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio006.wav",
      "text": "お風呂を上がったら服を着るのが当たり前よ！",
      "startTime": 66.9860067527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "冷静な莉央さんも",
      "startTime": 70.2753038724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui005.wav",
      "text": "ララさんのマイペースには勝てなかったわね……",
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4408.6311022000045
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr001.wav",
      "text": "モモちゃん？　こんな所で何をしてるんですか？",
      "startTime": 77.4086321195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "泊めてもらったお礼に、植物を植えていたんです",
      "startTime": 81.6752987862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
