      "text": "女子寮ですから防犯対策はしっかりしておかないと",
      "startTime": 85.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "植物って、その木ですか？　普通の木に見えますけど",
      "startTime": 90.3086346626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr002.wav",
      "text": "これが防犯対策になるんですか？",
      "startTime": 95.6666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい。この宇宙植物は、枝や根が触手のように動いて",
      "startTime": 98.5086346626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo002.wav",
      "text": "近づいた獲物を捕らえて武装解除させるんですよ",
      "startTime": 104.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おお！　宇宙の植物って凄いですね……！",
      "startTime": 108.4753008206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr003.wav",
      "text": "これは面白い悪戯が出来るかもです……！",
      "startTime": 113.0333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひょっとしてこころちゃんってそういうタイプですか？",
      "startTime": 116.7753008206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo003.wav",
      "text": "ふふふ……私達、意外と似ているのかもしれませんね",
      "startTime": 121.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ、似たもの同士ということで",
      "startTime": 127.3752972603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr004.wav",
      "text": "良かったら一緒に悪戯作戦会議しませんか？",
      "startTime": 130.3999908448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "後で、{user}さんが寮に",
      "startTime": 134.3086305936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr005.wav",
      "text": "来るんですけど、その時に……ごにょごにょごにょ……",
      "startTime": 135.8333241781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "面白そうですね。それなら思い切って、この植物で……",
      "startTime": 141.341963927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo004.wav",
      "text": "ごにょごにょごにょ……",
      "startTime": 146.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おお～、なるほど！",
      "startTime": 148.7752911568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr006.wav",
      "text": "ふふふ……なんだかモモちゃんとは気が合いそうです",
      "startTime": 151.4999847413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わあ！　美味しそうなお料理が沢山",
